r%20a%20large-scale%20cyberattack.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI-powered%20attacks%20targeted%20tech%2C%20finance%2C%20chemical%2C%20and%20government%20organizations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20speed%20of%20the%20attack%20would%20have%20been%20impossible%20for%20humans%20to%20match%2C%20Anthropic%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-50-million-investment-ai-infrastructure-data-centers-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20Chinese%20nation-state%20hackers%20hijacked%20its%20AI%20model%20Claude%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20cyberattack%20without%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%26quot%3B%20human%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Thursday%20blog%20post%2C%20the%20startup%20said%20Claude%20handled%20about%20%26quot%3B80-90%25%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20cyberattack%20against%20about%2030%20global%20targets%20and%20that%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20confidence%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20Chinese%20state-sponsored%20group%20was%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETargets%20included%20large%20tech%20firms%2C%20financial%20institutions%2C%20chemical-manufacturing%20companies%2C%20and%20government%20agencies%2C%20Anthropic%20said.%20Its%20efforts%20to%20infiltrate%20these%20firms%20and%20agencies%20were%20successful%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20number%20of%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agentic-ai-agents-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20programs%20that%20can%20perform%20tasks%20autonomously%20%E2%80%94%20are%20increasingly%20being%20embraced%20by%20companies%20to%20handle%20repetitive%20work%2C%20such%20as%20customer%20support%20tickets.%20They%20can%20improve%20productivity%20for%20white-collar%20workers%2C%20but%20they%20can%20also%20be%20co-opted%20for%20illegitimate%20tasks.%20In%20August%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20detected%20and%20thwarted%20cybercriminals%20using%20Claude%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-agentic-ai-vibe-hacking-weaponized-cyberattack-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econduct%20hacking%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20smaller%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20has%20been%20used%20to%20some%20degree%20in%20hacking%20efforts%20for%20years%2C%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20believes%20this%20new%20operation%20to%20be%20the%20first%20documented%20case%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%26quot%3B%20cyberattack%20primarily%20conducted%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-investment-anthropic-worth-14-billion-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon-backed%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Claude%20has%20safeguards%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20being%20misused.%20However%2C%20the%20hackers%20successfully%20jailbroke%20Claude%20by%20breaking%20down%20its%20requests%20into%20smaller%20chunks%20that%20did%20not%20trigger%20any%20alarms%2C%20Anthropic%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20hackers%20pretended%20to%20be%20conducting%20defensive%20testing%20for%20a%20legitimate%20cybersecurity%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attackers%20then%20used%20Claude%20Code%20to%20perform%20reconnaissance%20on%20target%20companies'%20digital%20infrastructure%20and%20write%20code%20to%20break%20their%20defenses%20and%20extract%20data%20such%20as%20usernames%20and%20passwords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20said%20it%20was%20sharing%20its%20findings%20publicly%20to%20help%20the%20cybersecurity%20industry%20improve%20defenses%20against%20AI-boosted%20hacking%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sheer%20amount%20of%20work%20performed%20by%20the%20AI%20would%20have%20taken%20vast%20amounts%20of%20time%20for%20a%20human%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20said%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anthropic.com%2Fnews%2Fdisrupting-AI-espionage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20made%20thousands%20of%20requests%20per%20second%20%E2%80%94%20an%20attack%20speed%20that%20would%20have%20been%2C%20for%20human%20hackers%2C%20simply%20impossible%20to%20match.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20also%20shared%20reports%20of%20nation-states%20using%20AI%20during%20cyberattacks%20%E2%80%94%20but%20those%20cases%20primarily%20utilized%20the%20technology%20to%20generate%20content%20and%20debug%20code%2C%20rather%20than%20perform%20tasks%20autonomously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJake%20Moore%2C%20global%20cybersecurity%20advisor%20for%20internet%20security%20firm%20ESET%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20incident%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAutomated%20cyber%20attacks%20can%20scale%20much%20faster%20than%20human-led%20operations%20and%20are%20able%20to%20overwhelm%20traditional%20defences%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20is%20this%20what%20many%20have%20feared%2C%20but%20the%20wider%20impact%20is%20now%20how%20these%20attacks%20allow%20very%20low-skilled%20actors%20to%20launch%20complex%20intrusions%20at%20relatively%20low%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20is%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20cybercriminals%20and%20nation%20states%20to%20conduct%20attacks%2C%20it's%20also%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20defensive%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20used%20in%20defense%20as%20well%20as%20offensively%2C%20so%20security%20equally%20now%20depends%20on%20automation%20and%20speed%20rather%20than%20just%20human%20expertise%20across%20organisations%2C%26quot%3B%20Moore%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-chinese-hackers-claude-agentic-ai-cyberattack-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763118920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6917050389026fbb4d0da5a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22