0The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20being%20a%20part%20of%20new%20ideas%20and%20more%20innovative%20ways%20of%20doing%20things.%20Thinking%20outside%20the%20box%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20and%20brainstorming%20%26quot%3Bhow%20can%20we%20do%20this%20better%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20the%20same%20when%20it%20came%20to%20buying%20a%20home%2C%20which%20I%20did%20in%20November%20with%20the%20help%20of%20AI.%20It%20was%20more%20important%20for%20me%20to%20be%20in%20control%20of%20the%20purchase%2C%20versus%20being%20afraid%20to%20use%20AI.%20Everything%20is%20online%20anyway%2C%20so%20why%20be%20afraid%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20already%20dealt%20with%20a%20buyer's%20agent%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20satisfied%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20part%20ways.%20I%20felt%20it%20would%20be%20easier%20for%20me%20just%20to%20buy%20my%20home%20myself%20if%20I%20could%20actually%20take%20more%20control%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22882%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20woman.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690cc6b17f37aa653f55844c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVicki%20Lynn%20wanted%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20herself%20and%20used%20AI%20to%20help.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Vicki%20Lynn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d8b1373-7c01-4f6f-af63-296685c6eaf9%5C%22%3EUsing%20an%20agent%20took%20too%20much%20time%20for%20me%20and%20involved%20too%20many%20added%20expenses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20aware%20that%20most%20sellers%20pay%20the%20buyer%20agent's%20commission%2C%20so%20that%20was%20even%20more%20incentive%20to%20go%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%20so%20I%20could%20potentially%20reap%20the%20financial%20benefits%20of%20not%20having%20an%20agent%20and%20get%20credit%20on%20closing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20agent%20told%20me%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnational-association-realtors-lawsuit-settlement-housing-market-homebuying-agents-commissions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20NAR%20settlement%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20I%20signed%20three%20contracts%20with%20an%20agent%20in%20less%20than%20six%20months.%20The%20first%20was%20in%20June%202025%2C%20when%20I%20flew%20to%20Florida%20quickly%20to%20look%20at%20some%20homes%20while%20I%20was%20still%20living%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20I%20would%20be%20liable%20for%203%25%20of%20the%20purchase%20price%20%E2%80%94%20although%20it's%20typically%20paid%20by%20the%20seller%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20were%20some%20fees%2C%20like%20%24300%20and%20%24400%20fees%20built%20in%20there%20for%20whatever%20agent%20fees%20and%20paperwork%20fees%20they%20throw%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20almost%20%24800%20total%20in%20just%20fees%20for%20her%20being%20a%20buyer's%20agent.%20I%20wasn't%20crazy%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20signed%20an%20agreement%20that%20said%20she%20would%20show%20me%20two%20homes.%20Then%20I%20signed%20another%20contract%20once%20I%20moved%20to%20Florida.%20Then%2C%20right%20before%20I%20was%20going%20to%20view%20three%20properties%20on%20a%20weekend%2C%20she%20said%2C%20after%20changes%20with%20her%20company%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20sign%20a%20contract%20for%20all%20of%20Florida%2C%20not%20just%20certain%20counties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20that.%20Can%20I%20just%20keep%20the%20contract%20for%20this%20neighborhood%3F%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20show%20me%20the%20properties%20if%20I%20didn't%20sign%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20house.%20I%20didn't%20care%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20signed%20it%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20don't%20find%20a%20home%20by%20December%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20stop%20looking.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20going%20to%20let%20the%20contract%20run%20out%20and%20start%20searching%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bffe84db-8254-466e-8694-d82f9a2832dd%5C%22%3EI%20was%20skeptical%20to%20have%20AI%20write%20up%20my%20contract%2C%20but%20it%20worked%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20found%20out%20about%20Homa%2C%20I%20had%20already%20found%20a%20home%20that%20I%20wanted.%20I%20knew%20the%20area%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20what%20the%20prices%20were%2C%20so%20I%20had%20already%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20work%20prior%20to%20Homa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20buyer%20who%20was%20ready%20to%20buy%2C%20and%20I%20was%20going%20to%20act%20quickly.%20If%20something%20checked%20all%20the%20boxes%2C%20then%20I%20was%20going%20to%20act%20on%20it%20with%20an%20offer%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoma%20helped%20me%20with%20the%20writeup%20of%20the%20contract.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20just%20go%20online%20and%20easily%20make%20an%20offer%2C%20put%20a%20closing%20date%2C%20and%20get%20all%20the%20information%20on%20the%20offer%2C%20and%20get%20the%20ball%20rolling%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listing%20price%20of%20the%20home%20I%20wanted%20to%20buy%20was%20%24316%2C000%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20I%20knew%20that.%20Because%20I'd%20done%20my%20research%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20worth%20it%2C%20and%20that%20if%20I%20undercut%20them%20too%20much%20on%20the%20asking%20price%2C%20I%20probably%20wouldn't%20get%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20offered%20what%20they%20were%20asking%2C%20and%20then%20I%20asked%20them%20for%20the%202.5%25%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20pay%20the%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20it%20came%20to%20%247%2C900%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20credit%20on%20the%20home%20instead.%20So%20that%20was%20also%20an%20incentive%20not%20to%20use%20an%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20possibly%20could%20have%20lost%20this%20sale%20had%20I%20been%20with%20the%20agent%20because%20the%20time%20it%20was%20taking%