e%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20simulating%203D%20worlds%3B%20and%20vGPU%2C%20which%20enables%20multiple%20workers%20to%20share%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20AI%20Enterprise%20is%20a%20suite%20of%20tools%20that%20helps%20clients%20make%20their%20own%20AI%20apps.%20It%20was%20launched%20in%202021%20and%20designed%20to%20run%20with%20Nvidia's%20AI%20chips%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-secret-sauce-regulators-gpu-chips-jensen-huang-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECUDA%2C%20a%20Nvidia%20software%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20allows%20the%20chips%20to%20handle%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20computing%20tasks.%20NVAIE's%20customer%20list%20includes%20Nasdaq%2C%20the%20IRS%2C%20and%20AT%26amp%3BT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20internal%20discussions%20focus%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20those%20Nvidia%20business%20software%20products%20%E2%80%94%20not%20CUDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd73aaa3-c26a-4f9e-a662-e28637292d48%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20software%20sales%20forecasts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20specializes%20in%20designing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGPUs%20and%20other%20AI%20hardware%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20the%20company's%20main%20business%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20break%20out%20revenues%20for%20business%20software%20in%20earnings%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20software%20is%20a%20smaller%20part%20of%20its%20business%2C%20it%20helps%20the%20company%20generate%20recurring%20revenue%20for%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20AI%20products%20across%20both%20hardware%20and%20software%20and%20deepen%20customer%20dependence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20hiccups%2C%20Nvidia%20is%20forecasting%20healthy%20software%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20internal%20email%2C%20sent%20in%20July%2C%20features%20a%20sales%20chart%20for%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%20fiscal%202026%20in%20North%20and%20Latin%20America%20that%20shows%20stand-alone%20software%20is%20projected%20to%20hit%20110%25%20of%20sales%20targets.%20Software%20sold%20alongside%20hardware%20was%20expected%20to%20reach%20only%2039%25%20of%20its%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20software%20sales%20forecasts%20were%20%2478.7%20million%20for%20the%20quarter%2C%20driven%20by%20NVAIE%2C%20which%20was%20forecast%20to%20hit%20186%25%20of%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cd93abf-e674-443e-8c42-ee1741b100c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'fundamental%20disconnect'%20with%20Nvidia%20customers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20July%20email%20states%20Nvidia's%20sales%20partners%20and%20account%20managers%20need%20to%20develop%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20software%20story%26quot%3B%20around%20NVAIE%20and%20other%20software%20products.%20It%20mentions%20plans%20to%20create%20a%20workshop%20for%20customers%20to%20use%20NVAIE%20and%20other%20product%20libraries%20to%20plan%20potential%20AI%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20in%20August%20detailed%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20education%20%E2%80%94%20both%20internally%20and%20when%20negotiating%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBiggest%20pain%20point%20will%20be%20educating%20%5Ba%20prospective%20client's%5D%20procurement%20and%20legal%20teams%20on%20what%20our%20AI%20Enterprise%20software%20is%2Fisn't%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20August%20email%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20email%20also%20says%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20disconnect%26quot%3B%20between%20Nvidia%20and%20clients'%20legal%20and%20procurement%20teams%20in%20understanding%20Nvidia's%20software%20sales%20processes%20during%20negotiations%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20within%20highly%20regulated%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20finance%20and%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20security%20and%20indemnity%20obligations%2C%20which%20are%20Nvidia's%20legal%20responsibility%20in%20the%20event%20that%20a%20client%20is%20sued%2C%20were%20other%20sticking%20points%20in%20negotiations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20August%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20concerns%20included%20requesting%20higher%20damages%20caps%20%E2%80%94%20the%20maximum%20amount%20that%20Nvidia%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20if%20something%20goes%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20than%20Nvidia%20is%20comfortable%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20far%20from%20alone%20in%20contending%20with%20uneven%20AI%20adoption%2C%20as%20some%20companies%20view%20the%20white-hot%20technology%20as%20too%20early%20to%20deploy%20widely%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-impact-job-losses-layoffs-productivity-cost-cutting-goldman-sachs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agweiss%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egweiss%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40geoffweiss.25.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-internal-emails-software-sales-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763114401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69164c3389026fbb4d0d9fba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-internal-emails-software-sales-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia's%20AI%20software%20sales%20team%20faces%20some%20challeng