%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20AI%20cloud%20data%20center%20racks%20with%20servers%2C%20cables%2C%20and%20blinking%20lights%20represents%20advanced%20computing%20power%2C%20big%20data%20processing%2C%20and%20cloud%20technology%20infrastructure%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6916b47dabd5e944effab9d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20leads%20the%20world%20in%20AI%2C%20but%20its%20power%20grid%20could%20hold%20it%20back.%3Cp%3EJoan%20Cros%2FNurPhoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20is%20leading%20the%20AI%20revolution%2C%20but%20power%20shortages%20could%20slow%20its%20progress%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20warns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EData%20centers%20already%20consume%206%25%20of%20US%20electricity%20and%20could%20draw%20nearly%20twice%20that%20by%202030.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20massive%20expansion%20of%20spare%20power%20may%20give%20it%20a%20powerful%20edge%20in%20the%20global%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20racing%20ahead%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20its%20biggest%20obstacle%20is%20more%20than%20chips%2C%20rare%20earths%2C%20or%20talent%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20electricity%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20power%20grid%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20already%20straining%20under%20the%20surge%20of%20data%20centers%20fueling%20AI%20models%2C%20with%20these%20massive%20facilities%20now%20accounting%20for%20about%206%25%20of%20total%20US%20electricity%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20share%20is%20expected%20to%20nearly%20double%20to%2011%25%20by%202030%2C%20pushing%20parts%20of%20the%20country's%20