0data%20center%20power%20demand%20growth%20while%20supporting%20demand%20in%20other%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman's%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20buildup%20follows%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-power-shortage-halts-apple-tesla-suppliers-stresses-supply-chain-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenergy%20crunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20that%20led%20Beijing%20to%20ramp%20up%20power%20generation%20across%20renewables%2C%20natural%20gas%2C%20nuclear%2C%20and%20coal%20to%20ensure%20energy%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20is%20retiring%20coal%20plants%20faster%20than%20it's%20adding%20new%20natural%20gas%20or%20renewable%20capacity.%20Other%20issues%20that%20could%20limit%20data%20center%20growth%20in%20the%20US%20include%20lengthy%20project%20timelines%20and%20a%20global%20shortage%20of%20gas-powered%20turbines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReliable%20and%20ample%20power%20supply%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20key%20factor%20shaping%20this%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20because%20power%20infrastructure%20bottlenecks%20can%20be%20slow%20to%20solve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20report%20came%20amid%20an%20intensifying%20race%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-warning-us-china-ai-tech-competition-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20mentioned%20energy%20as%20an%20issue%20that%20could%20hinder%20the%20US's%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20Financial%20Times%2C%20Huang%20noted%20a%20growing%20wave%20of%20AI%20regulations%20emerging%20across%20US%20states%20and%20warned%20that%20too%20many%20new%20rules%20could%20stifle%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20he%20said%20China's%20government%20energ